<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Petrus Wacker, königlicher Hofschreiber</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Nachrichten aus Ungarn.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_505" id="252r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_505_r1l11">Petro wacker </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_505_r1l12"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Peter / VVir <expan>bıt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>freuntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> / ob Jr ıcht newer vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_505_r1l13">fremder leuff oder mer danyden cʒu <expan>vng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> höret / oder vveſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_505_r1l14">daʒ Jr vns die an <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> brief <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> wiſſen laſſen vvöllet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_505_r1l15"><expan>Alſu<ex>er</ex>re</expan> ew das füglıch ſeẏ / das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſıg<ex>elt</ex></expan> vnter </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_505_r1l16">Sebolt Pfincʒings <expan>Jnſ<ex>igel</ex></expan> / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_505" id="252r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Petro Wacker</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Peter, wir <expan>bit<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>freuntl<ex>ich,</ex></expan> ob ir icht newer und fremder leuff oder
                        mer danyden czu <expan>Ung<ex>er</ex>n</expan> höret oder west, daz ir uns
                        die an <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> brief
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> wissen lassen wöllet,
                                <expan>alsv<ex>er</ex>re</expan> ew das füglich sey. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.
                                <expan>V<ex>er</ex>sig<ex>elt</ex></expan> unter Sebolt Pfinczings
                                <expan>ins<ex>igel</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
